No. 917,

Misc.

Armijo v. United States. James F. Hewitt for petitioner. Solicitor General Griswold, Assistant Attorney General Vinson and Jerome M. Feit for the United States.

C. A. 9th Cir. Certiorari denied.

Mr. Justice Black and Mr. Justice Douglas are of the opinion that certiorari should be granted and the judgment reversed.
